資本化的可能結果為何？（15 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "340fd4aa51e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "305", "s": "1008", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "租稅各論", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-6f0ba476-moex-00202', 'disabled-6f0ba476', 'disabled-6f0ba476-moex-113-3e700a6a', 'sub-disabled-6f0ba476-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '華格納的租稅課徵原則中，有關課稅平等原則的概念相當於下列何者？', '["相等絕對犧牲", "絕對公平原則", "受益原則", "量能原則"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "340fd4aa51e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2b16893eca27", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "305", "s": "1008", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "租稅各論", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-6f0ba476-moex-00203', 'disabled-6f0ba476', 'disabled-6f0ba476-moex-113-3e700a6a', 'sub-disabled-6f0ba476-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '政府課徵一種稅目替代另一種稅目，而維持稅收不變之租稅歸宿分析，稱為：', '["差異性租稅歸宿分析", "平衡預算歸宿分析", "租稅增額歸宿分析", "平衡成長歸宿分析"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "340fd4aa51e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2b16893eca27", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "305", "s": "1008", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "租稅各論", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-6f0ba476-moex-00204', 'disabled-6f0ba476', 'disabled-6f0ba476-moex-113-3e700a6a', 'sub-disabled-6f0ba476-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '一個小型開放經濟體的資本市場上，資本需求曲線為負斜率，價格為市場利 率。其他條件不變時，有關政府課徵定額（specific）資本稅之敘述，下列何 者正確？', '["供給者得到的利率下降", "需求曲線下移幅度等於稅額", "均衡資本交易量不變", "供給者負擔所有的稅負"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "340fd4aa51e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2b16893eca27", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "305", "s": "1008", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "租稅各論", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-6f0ba476-moex-00205', 'disabled-6f0ba476', 'disabled-6f0ba476-moex-113-3e700a6a', 'sub-disabled-6f0ba476-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '在 Harberger 模型假設下，有食品及製造二部門，若製造部門為相對勞動密 集，政府對製造部門的資本課稅，當產出效果小於要素替代效果，則利率相 對於工資率的比率將會如何變化？', '["上升", "不變", "下降", "無法判斷"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "340fd4aa51e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2b16893eca27", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "305", "s": "1008", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "租稅各論", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-6f0ba476-moex-00206', 'disabled-6f0ba476', 'disabled-6f0ba476-moex-113-3e700a6a', 'sub-disabled-6f0ba476-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '一般而言，皮古稅（Pigouvian tax）的課徵可以改善效率，但亦可能藉由下 列何種效果造成效率傷害？', '["雙重紅利效果（double-dividendeffect）", "內部化效果（internalization）", "租稅相互作用效果（tax-interactioneffect）", "中立性效果（neutralityeffect）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "340fd4aa51e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2b16893eca27", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "305", "s": "1008", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "租稅各論", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-6f0ba476-moex-00207', 'disabled-6f0ba476', 'disabled-6f0ba476-moex-113-3e700a6a', 'sub-disabled-6f0ba476-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者最有可能產生超額負擔？', '["課徵土地稅", "對食物補貼", "課徵人頭稅", "對追求利潤最大的獨占廠商課徵利潤稅"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "340fd4aa51e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2b16893eca27", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "305", "s": "1008", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "租稅各論", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-6f0ba476-moex-00208', 'disabled-6f0ba476', 'disabled-6f0ba476-moex-113-3e700a6a', 'sub-disabled-6f0ba476-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '在勞動市場為完全競爭下，當勞工的受補償勞動供給曲線為正斜率，而廠商 是市場工資的接受者時，對廠商發放的工資課徵從價稅，會產生何種結果？', '["當工資稅率愈高，則課稅所產生的超額負擔愈低", "當受補償的勞動供給彈性愈高，則課稅所產生的超額負擔愈高", "政府收到的稅收會超過福利損失", "政府收到的稅收會等於福利損失"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "340fd4aa51e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2b16893eca27", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "305", "s": "1008", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "租稅各論", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-6f0ba476-moex-00209', 'disabled-6f0ba476', 'disabled-6f0ba476-moex-113-3e700a6a', 'sub-disabled-6f0ba476-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關最適稅制（optimaltaxsystem）之敘述，下列何者正確？', '["稅種愈少愈好的稅制", "稅收愈多愈好的稅制", "符合租稅公平與效率的稅制", "極大化社會福利的稅制"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "340fd4aa51e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2b16893eca27", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "305", "s": "1008", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "租稅各論", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-6f0ba476-moex-00210', 'disabled-6f0ba476', 'disabled-6f0ba476-moex-113-3e700a6a', 'sub-disabled-6f0ba476-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '當個人為固定所得下，如何對所消費的兩種財貨課稅以達到租稅中立性原', '["不改變財貨的消費量", "不改變財貨的相對價格", "不產生所得效 果", "不產生替代效果  ⑤不改變財貨邊際效用的相對關係"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "340fd4aa51e1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2b16893eca27", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "305", "s": "1008", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "租稅各論", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
